      "$value": "AkkuratLL",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Primary workhorse — body text, navigation, buttons, labels, UI chrome. Weight 400 for body, 500 for labels, 700 for emphasis. Light weights (200/300) appear in large display sizes for an airy editorial feel. Custom alternative: Inter, Neue Haas Grotesk, or Söhne."
